-- EUROPE RESEARCH ROUNDUP- Novo Nordisk, Reed Elsevier
-- 
-- Tue Dec 30, 2014 09:53AM EST
-- None



Dec 30 (Reuters) - Securities analysts revised their ratings and price targets on several European companies, including Novo Nordisk and Reed Elsevier, on Tuesday.

HIGHLIGHTS * Novo Nordisk <NOVOb.CO>: Bryan Garnier cuts fair value to Dkk 273 from Dkk 296; rating buy * Reed Elsevier <ELSN.AS>: KBC raises target to 20.50 euros from 16 euros; rating accumulate   Following is a summary of research actions on European companies reported by Reuters on Tuesday. Stock entries are in alphabetical order. * Nokian Tyres <NRE1V.HE>: Nordea Equity cuts target price to eur 27 from eur 30; rating buy * Novo Nordisk <NOVOb.CO>: Bryan Garnier cuts fair value to Dkk 273 from Dkk 296; rating buy * Reed Elsevier <ELSN.AS>: KBC raises target to 20.50 euros from 16 euros; rating accumulate * Swiss Re <SRENH.VX>: JP Morgan raises target to sfr 81 from sfr 77; rating underweight